snippet.title: Johnny Depp Finally Speaks On Defeating Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp Finally Speaks On Defeating Amber Heard

Did Johnny Depp just defeat Amber Heard?
Good news for Johnny Depp fans: the actor is one step closer to winning the high-profile defamation case against ex-wife Amber Heard and he’s now determined to prove that Amber lied when she accused him of domestic violence in her infamous 2018 Washington Post op-ed.

However, we’re also hearing that Johnny is afraid that Hollywood has already blacklisted him and that his career may never recover.
So what’s going on with Johnny and Amber’s legal battle? Will Johnny finally be able to prove his innocence? And if he does, will Hollywood welcome him back?

It’s been a while since we heard any updates on Johnny Depp and Amber Heard’s messy court battle but that doesn’t mean the drama between the former spouses is over.
In fact, the already messy divorce saga has just gotten even messier after Johnny scored a rare legal victory over Amber.
